request.description:
List products. Public. No auth.

**Query params:** `page` (default 1), `limit` (default 20), optional `categoryId` (UUID), `isActive` (true), `requiresApproval` (true).

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "products": [
    { "id": "uuid", "name": "Product Name", "slug": "product-name", "categoryId": "...", "requiresApproval": false, "variants": [...] }
  ],
  "pagination": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 50, "totalPages": 3 }
}
```

Get current user's cart with items. Requires `Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}`.

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "cart": {
    "items": [
      {
        "id": "cart-item-uuid",
        "productVariantId": "variant-uuid",
        "quantity": 2,
        "product": { "name": "Product Name", "...": "..." },
        "variant": { "packSize": "30 tablets", "price": "25.99" }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```
Empty cart: `{ "cart": { "items": [] } }`.
